

1 T-wepnag mam am kih Thessalonica t am: 

Am ant ep wo i em-oꞌohani ahni Paul. K ia ni-wehmaj g Silas ch Timothy k ch am i ni-wehmaj. 

Dam woho hemajkamgaj g t-ohg Jiosh ab i e dagitok t-kownalig Jesus Christ wui. 

2 Ab o wa si s-em-hoꞌigeꞌid g t-ohg Jiosh g t-kownalig Jesus Christ wehm ch ab wo wa baꞌich i em-mahkad g i wehmtadag ch s-ap tahhadkam. 

**Matsh hekid wo i e ai g geꞌe lodaita **

3 Chum ach hekid ab si hoꞌigeꞌid g Jiosh em-hekaj, t-wepnag. Am amsh si i gewkahim e-wohochudadag ed ch baꞌich i si pihk e elid ab aꞌai e wui. 4 Kuch heg hekaj si s-ap t-tahtk ch wehsko ha ahgidahim g t-wehm wohochuddam ab em-amjed. Msh am em-shoꞌigchud nam pi ab s-wohochud g Jiosh. Kumsh eda s-ap ab nakog g e-shoꞌigdag am wehhejed g Jiosh. 5 Id o am wohokamchud mat am i em-apꞌech g Jiosh e wehhejed k pi ab hu haꞌichu wo em-abch am lodaita ch ed. Am am e shoꞌigchud wehhejed g Jiosh kownaltalig. K g Jiosh hab em-elid mam d s-apꞌekam ch am wo i em-wahpki e-kihdag ed. 6 Jiosh at s-ap hab wo juh g lodaita. Hegam mo em-shoꞌigchud at wo e shoꞌigch heg hekaj. 7 Kumt ahpim wo e doꞌibia ab amjed g e-shoꞌigchudadag. Jiosh at hab wo juh ihda mat hekid ep wo jiwia g t-kownalig Jesus ab dahm kahchim t amjed. T ia wehmaj wo dada g anghiligaj k wo si s-gewkdagk. 8 T ia wehmaj ep wo e chehgi g si geꞌe mei. T wo s-koꞌokam ha namkid g Jesus hegam mo pi mahch g Jiosh ch pi ab hu wohog elid g s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj ab amjed g t-kownalig Jesus. 9 Hegam at gam hu wo si i e gawulkai ab amjed g Jiosh k pi hekid wo bei g geꞌe gewkdaj k chum hekid ab wo beihid g s-koꞌok e-namkidadag. 10 Id at hab wo e juh mat hekid ia ep wo jiwia g t-kownalig Jesus. Kut g gewkdaj am haha wo i chehgi mat t-doꞌibia k ab i t-gawulkai e wehhejed. 

11 Pegih, heg ach hekaj chum hekid ab t-hoꞌigeꞌidahun Jiosh wui am em-wehhejed. Ab at i em-wai mamt wo e doꞌibia k d wo aꞌaligajk. M hab hahawa s-junimk g s-apꞌekam ab s-wohochudch. Kuch ab tahni g Jiosh mat am e-tatchui oidk hab wo em-juh k hab s-ap hab wo em-elidad. Jiosh o gewkdag mat hab wo juh ihda mach ab tahni. 12 Kumt ab wo si haꞌichuchudad g t-kownalig Jesus. T heg hab waꞌap ab wo si em-haꞌichuchudad. Jiosh at si s-hemajim am i apꞌech g e-alidag wehm mat id hab wo em-juni. 

